.org/resource/Tribe_of_Reuben\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tribe_of_Reuben\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Wrestlers\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"68kg\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"57kg\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"76kg\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are reigning African champions and debutants, Esther Kolawole (62kg) and Ogunsanya Christinah (53kg), while Ashton Mutuwa completes the list in the (125kg) men's freestyle wrestling.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashton-under-Lyne\", \"score\": 0.9507738988175903, \"rank\": 0.05177477131340826, \"text\": \"Ashton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashton-under-Lyne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashton-under-Lyne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"African champions\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"debutants\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"62kg\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"the (125kg) men's freestyle wrestling\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coaches are Victor Kodei, Purity Akuh and Happiness Burutu.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Talking_Machine_Company\", \"score\": 0.6358841260229078, \"rank\": 0.4045114875164883, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Talking_Machine_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Talking_Machine_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burutu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Burutu\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wik